title: Graybeards 2022 with Evan Silva
itunes:title: Graybeards 2022 with Evan Silva
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Colleen Wolfe take you through all of the latest NFL news including the tragic loss of Dwayne Haskins at 24 years old. Evan Silva joins the show to go over Dan Hanzus's Graybeards roster. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
